ADDITIONAL NOTICES:

ServiceNow Integration:
This software connects to ServiceNow instances. Use of ServiceNow requires
appropriate licenses from ServiceNow, Inc. This software does not include or
provide ServiceNow licenses. Users must ensure they have proper authorization
and licensing to access their ServiceNow instances.

Third-Party Services:
This software integrates with third-party LLM services (OpenAI, Anthropic,
Google, Azure). Users are responsible for obtaining their own API keys and
complying with the respective service providers' terms of service.
